  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary</strong></p><p>We are looking for an experienced tipper truck driver who can maintain the vehicle in good working condition and operate efficiently at job sites.</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform regular vehicle inspections and maintenance to ensure safe and reliable operation of the tipper truck</li><li>Operate the tipper truck safely and efficiently according to job site requirements and regulations</li><li>Navigate and maneuver the vehicle on various job site terrains to deliver materials as needed</li><li>Communicate effectively with team members and site supervisors to coordinate deliveries and operations</li><li>Follow safety protocols to maintain a safe work environment for self and others at the job site</li></ul>",
